    {
      "id": "1503365064902578216",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2026-05-11T11:56:02.645+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Here is what my working control section looks like: \n\n``` \n.control\nsave all\nnoise v(out,vss) vin dec 10 100 1e6 1\nprint inoise_total\nprint all\nsetplot noise1\ngnuplot p1 inoise_spectrum\n.endc\n```",
      "author": {
